{
  "text": "The results so far have shown that DOF may increase spatio-temporal complexity. But also both spatially and temporally ordered regimes can be obtained by applying DOF. To demonstrate this (1) (t) (solid curve) and I (2) (t) (dashed curve) in the centers of laserstripe 1 and laser-stripe 2, respectively. effect, we start with a regime where the TSL shows chaotic behavior in absence of DOF (Fig. 13) ; this state is typical for a TSL being moderately coupled at an increased interelement separation (here s = 6.0 \u00b5m) [CITATION_1] .",
